data-text=\"decurioni\" data-n=\"95\" data-lemma=\"\">DECURIONI</span><span data-text=\"bus\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"\">[...]</span><br id=\"al10-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">10</span><span data-text=\"quini\" data-n=\"105\" data-lemma=\"\">QUINI</span><span data-text=\"denarii\" data-n=\"110\" data-lemma=\"\">DEN[....]</span><br id=\"al11-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">11</span><span data-text=\"dati\" data-n=\"115\" data-lemma=\"\">DATI</span><span data-text=\"sunt\" data-n=\"120\" data-lemma=\"\">SUNT</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic000100_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic000100_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000100.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic000100-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text from autopsy</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-8417-7089\">Tuuli Ahlholm</a></p>  <p>To Antia Cleopatra, daughter of Marcus, priestess, by the will of the people, (erected) by decree of the city council, with the expense reimbursed from public funds. On the occasion of whose dedication (?) one denarius was given to (each of) the plebs, two to the sons of decuriones, and five to the decuriones.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Mommsen 1883 <a href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/650796\" target=\"_blank\">7352</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589</a>  </li><li> Mommsen 1883 <a href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\" target=\"_blank\">7352add</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 1988 tav.16 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427</a>  </li><li> Bivona 1994 18 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002137</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>regular letters iwth a faily wide square module, lacking visible interpuncts or serifs (but note the material); use of ligature at the end of line 2.</p> Line 1  55  Line 2-4  53-54  Line 5  48-52  Line 6-8  50-54  Line 9  48-54  Line 10-11  50-54  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
